List of pins and peripherials used in this project

GPIOA:
PA0     ------> ADC1
PA1     ------> ADC1
PA2     ------> USART2_TX
PA3     ------> USART2_RX
PA10    ------> OUTPUT, EANABLING AND DISABLING FAN

GPIOB:
PB4     ------> BUTTON FOR DECREASING TEMPERATURE THRESHOLD
PB5     ------> BUTTON FOR INCREASING TEMPERATURE THRESHOLD
PB6     ------> I2C1_SCL
PB7     ------> I2C1_SDA


List of peripherials used:
ADC1     ------> MEASURING VOLTAGE DROP ON TEMPERATURE SENSOR
I2C1     ------> SENDING DATA TO BE DISPLAYED ON LCD
TIM6     ------> ENABLING ADC EVERY A PERIOD OF TIME
TIM5     ------> TRANSMITTING DATA TO HC-05 EVERY A PERIOD OF TIME
TIM4     ------> REFRESHING LCD EVERY A PERIOD OF TIME